 the management for performance review. 8. Stay up to date with industry-related news and tech from both international and local channels to be shared with team members. 9. Basic translation work on marketing collateral from central communications to meet the local community needs. --- Candidate Requirements: 1. Proven work experience in the fields of marketing/business development. 2. Knowledge in digital assets (cryptocurrency) and margin trading is required. 3. Great interpersonal and communication skills. Proficient in computer skills and MS Office software. 4. Able to communicate, read and write well in both Bahasa Indonesia and English. 5. Basic design and layout skills would be a plus point. 6. Experienced in social media management and marketing. 7. Highly self motivated and able to work independently without being micro-managed. 8. Attention to detail, critical thinking and a great problem solver. 9. Constantly thinking of ideas to disrupt industry. Skills Networking, Social Media Marketing, Business Development Compensation 1000 "
